CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784744311
OL,3,CMan accused of double murder in
OL,4,CCornwall says alleged victim lived
OL,5,Cwith him
OL,7,FThe man accused of the murder of two
OL,8,Fmen on his land at Sticker in Cornwall
OL,9,Fsaid one of them was living with him
OL,10,Fon the land in the days after he was
OL,11,Flast seen alive.
OL,13,FJames Desborough told the jury in his
OL,14,Ftrial at Winchester Crown Court that
OL,15,FClaudio Aquilino had gone back to the
OL,16,Fwoods in Sticker with him after they
OL,17,Fhad both been evicted from the Sandy
OL,18,FLodge Hotel in Newquay.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784744311
OL,3,CMan accused of double murder in
OL,4,CCornwall says alleged victim lived
OL,5,Cwith him
OL,7,FHe said the two of them had met up in
OL,8,FNewquay and Claudio had got him to
OL,9,Ftake crack.
OL,11,FHe said they had gone back to the
OL,12,Fwoods and had slept, smoked weed,
OL,13,Featen and talked about old movies. He
OL,14,Fsaid Claudio had fixed an old bike he
OL,15,Fhad there.
OL,17,FAsked by the prosecution why he had
OL,18,Fsent a message to a friend about a
OL,19,F"crackhead finally leaving" the woods
OL,20,Fhe admitted he had had an argument
OL,21,Fwith Claudio that day.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784744311
OL,3,CMan accused of double murder in
OL,4,CCornwall says alleged victim lived
OL,5,Cwith him
OL,7,F"I did have an argument with Claudio
OL,8,Fthat day. But Claudio was alive and
OL,9,Fwas on the bike when I got back," he
OL,10,Freplied.
OL,12,FDesborough was asked about using
OL,13,FClaudio Aquilino's bank card after he
OL,14,Fwas last seen alive. He told the jury
OL,15,Fhe'd been given permission by Claudio
OL,16,Fto use the card. He said that Claudio
OL,17,Fused his money as well, he described
OL,18,Fhim as a good friend.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784744311
OL,3,CMan accused of double murder in
OL,4,CCornwall says alleged victim lived
OL,5,Cwith him
OL,7,FMoving on to questions about Daniel
OL,8,FColeman, Mr Desborough said they too
OL,9,Fhad been friends.
OL,11,FHe admitted that he had slept with Mr
OL,12,FColeman's wife while they were at the
OL,13,FSandy Lodge Hotel but said he had no
OL,14,Finterest in Hannah Coleman, he said he
OL,15,Fand Daniel Coleman had shaken hands
OL,16,Fand "were fine."
OL,18,FAsked whether he wanted Daniel Coleman
OL,19,Fout of the way because he still had a
OL,20,Fsexual interest in Hannah Coleman, he
OL,21,Freplied, 'No."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784744311
OL,3,CMan accused of double murder in
OL,4,CCornwall says alleged victim lived
OL,5,Cwith him
OL,7,FIn relation to evidence given by
OL,8,Fanother man Craig Cudmore, who said
OL,9,FJames Desborough after an argument
OL,10,Finvolving Dan and Hannah Coleman had
OL,11,Fsaid "somebody else is going to get
OL,12,Fburied," on the land at Sticker, he
OL,13,Fsaid: "I never threatened Dan. I never
OL,14,Fsaid somebody else is going to get
OL,15,Fburied in the woods. I did not say
OL,16,Fthat."
OL,18,FProsecutor Ahmed Hossain KC repled:
OL,19,F"But Daniel Coleman did get buried in
OL,20,Fthe woods didn't he, by you?"
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784744311
OL,3,CMan accused of double murder in
OL,4,CCornwall says alleged victim lived
OL,5,Cwith him
OL,7,F"Yes," replied Mr Desborough.
OL,9,FThe defendant was asked about an email
OL,10,Fhe had sent to the Petrocs service in
OL,11,FCornwall in which he had talked about
OL,12,Fvulnerable homeless people living on
OL,13,Fhis land including a husband and wife
OL,14,Fand had said he was "massively
OL,15,Fconcerned about her estranged husband
OL,16,Fand his controlling behaviour" and was
OL,17,Fgoing to "forcibly remove him from my
OL,18,Fproperty."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784744311
OL,3,CMan accused of double murder in
OL,4,CCornwall says alleged victim lived
OL,5,Cwith him
OL,7,FMr Desborough said he had clearly been
OL,8,Fdrunk when he wrote the email and said
OL,9,Fit was not serious.
OL,11,FHe said that other text messages where
OL,12,Fhe described being "fuming" and
OL,13,F"absolutely bloodthirsty" about the
OL,14,Fpeople living on his land were sent
OL,15,Fwhen he was obviously upset.
OL,17,FJames Desborough denies the murder of
OL,18,FClaudio Aquilino and a second man
OL,19,FDaniel Coleman. He admits failing to
OL,20,Fallow the lawful burial of the two men.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
